server <- function(input, output, session) {}
ui <- fluidPage(
 
  titlePanel("using Tabsets"), # our title
  sidebarLayout(
    
    sidebarPanel(
      sliderInput(inputId = "s1",
                  label = "My Slider",
                  value = 1, min = 1, max = 20),
      checkboxGroupInput("checkGroup", label = h3("Race"), 
    choices = list("white" = 1, "black" = 2, "Choice 3" = 3),
    selected = 1)
    ),
    
    mainPanel(
      tabsetPanel(
        tabPanel("Tab1", "Any text needs to be in quotes"),
        tabPanel("Tab2", "Second Tab"),
        tabPanel("Citations with the blockquote tag", "R is Great")
      )
    )
  )
)
shinyApp(ui = ui, server = server)
